latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Mother’s Day!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here is "𝐀 𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐟𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐲𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫" 

Despite us being granted the guise of God himself, we have always taken and taken from our mothers. The current youth has gone taciturn over noticing and appreciating the efforts and the sacrifices of their mothers. 
It's your turn to gift your mom the love, recognition and appreciation that she has deserved all her life.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Valentine’s day special....
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
"Everything I understand, I understand only because I love" - Leo Tolstoy 
To celebrate the emotion celebrated by great men for centuries known we curated a few evenings to remember. 

In all these years one thing that we have always aspired to do is keep our guests happy, so we curated this event to spread joy and celebrate love with everyone.

It was an absolute pleasure having @drashtii_patwaa , @diyajagani @keyurvaghela_mr.karan , managed by @allegroschoolofmusicsurat  of  @rjrahill and @zaroon_talreja for entertaining all our beautiful guests with his charm. 

We are grateful to each and everyone who made this evening what it was.
